            <lg xml:id="TK1276">
<l>peritāṟṟip peṭpak kalatta laritāṟṟi</l>
<l>yaṉpiṉmai cūḻva tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The embrace that fills me with comfort and gladness is capable of enduring (my former) sorrow and meditating on his want of love.</l>
